<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<entry xmlns:functx="http://www.functx.com" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_boʒ"
    xml:lang="os">
    <form type="lemma"><orth>boʒ</orth><form type="variant"><orth>boʒo</orth></form><form
            type="variant"><orth>boʒol</orth></form></form>
    <sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
            <q>козел</q>
        </cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <q>goat</q>
        </cit></sense>
    <re><form type="lemma"><orth>cæw-boʒo</orth></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>козел</q>
            </cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>billy-goat</q>
            </cit></sense></re>
    <cit type="exampleGroup">
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>mænæ dyn ūj mæ fosy kʼord, mænæ dyn ūj ta boʒol, sæ razʒog sæǧ</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>вот тебе стадо моей баранты, а вот тебе %sбодзол%s, их козел-вожак</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>here is the flock of my sheep and here is %sboʒol%s, its goat-leader</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl><ref target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>IV 140</biblScope></bibl>
        </cit>
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>boʒol jæ styr sykʼatæ batīly</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>козел потрясает своими большими рогами</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>the billy-goat is shaking its big horns</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl><ref target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>IV 14</biblScope></bibl>
        </cit>
        <cit type="example" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
            <usg type="dialect"><lang/></usg>
            <quote>wælæ i xonxi særi cæw-boʒo xezuj</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>вон на горе пасется козел %sбодзо%s</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>there is a goat-%sboʒo%s is grazing on the hill</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl><ref target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II 135</biblScope></bibl>
        </cit>
    </cit>
    <cit type="exampleGroup">
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>mænæ dyn ūj mæ fosy kʼord, mænæ dyn ūj ta boʒol, sæ razʒog sæǧ</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>вот тебе стадо моей баранты, а вот тебе %sбодзол%s, их козел-вожак</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>here is the flock of my sheep and here is %sboʒol%s, its goat-leader</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl><ref target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>IV 140</biblScope></bibl>
        </cit>
        <cit type="example">
            <quote>boʒol jæ styr sykʼatæ batīly</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>козел потрясает своими большими рогами</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>the billy-goat is shaking its big horns</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl><ref target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>IV 14</biblScope></bibl>
        </cit>
        <cit type="example" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
            <usg type="dialect"><lang/></usg>
            <quote>wælæ i xonxi særi cæw-boʒo xezuj</quote>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <q>вон на горе пасется козел %sбодзо%s</q>
            </cit>
            <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <q>there is a goat-%sboʒo%s is grazing on the hill</q>
            </cit>
            <bibl><ref target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II 135</biblScope></bibl>
        </cit>
    </cit>
    <etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>būza-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>buz</w><gloss><q>козел</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="fa-x-dial"><lang/><w>boča</w><gloss><q>козочка</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="wbl"><lang/><w>buč</w><gloss><q>козел</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="xcl"><lang/><w>buc</w><gloss><q>ягненок</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="goh"><lang/><w>boc</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                ><lang/><w>Bock</w><gloss><q>козел</q></gloss></mentioned>. Невыдержанность звуковой
        формы (%iʒ%i вместо %iz%i, огласовка %iо%i в обоих диалектах) объясняется, возможно,
        экспрессивным употреблением в качестве клички.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>būza-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>buz</w><gloss><q>billy</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="fa-x-dial"><lang/><w>boča</w><gloss><q>little goat</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="wbl"><lang/><w>buč</w><gloss><q>billy</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="xcl"><lang/><w>buc</w><gloss><q>lamb</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="goh"><lang/><w>boc</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                ><lang/><w>Bock</w><gloss><q>billy</q></gloss></mentioned>. The inconsistency of the
        phonetics (%iʒ%i instead of %iz%i, vowel %iо%i in both dialects) is explained, probably, by
        the fact that it is used expressively as a nickname.</etym>
</entry>
